snippet.textDisplay:
Our partition cost us dearly
River Chenab often asks her sister River Ravi, how is my dear brother River Satluj ❤️

The Diamond lines

My grandfather belonged to Depalpur in Okara district of Punjab before partition. I grew up listening to stories of partition and the united Punjab that existed before that. 
He always wished to visit Depalpur once in his life again but never made it. Thousands of such unaccomplished wishes 💔

Long live Punjab 🇮🇳🇵🇰
